{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "22", "m": "05", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "10", "M": "39", "S": "45"}}, "news": [{"title": "Ashiana Housing to invest \u20b9186 crore in first phase of Jaipur project", "para": "Ashiana Housing has announced the launch of the first phase of Ashiana Oma, a residential project in Mansarovar Extension, Jaipur. The first phase will comprise 280 units and involve an estimated investment of \u20b9186.78 crore, while the overall project is planned across 10.35 acres with 490 units and an estimated project cost of \u20b9558.60 crore.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/ashiana-housing-unveils-186-crore-investment-in-jaipurs-ashiana-oma-project/131261814?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-26660/131261814.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "99acres reports loss before tax of \u20b959.15 crore in FY26", "para": "Info Edge's 99acres division reported a FY26 pre-tax loss of \u20b959.15 crore, despite an 18.81% revenue jump to \u20b9488.05 crore. Meanwhile, Info Edge's consolidated net profit surged 34.58% to \u20b91,762.84 crore in FY26, with total income rising 10.72% to \u20b94,343.28 crore. The board proposed a \u20b93.60 dividend.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/allied-industries/99acres-reports-significant-loss-before-tax-in-fy26-despite-revenue-growth/131261996?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-15140/131261996.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "allied-industries"}, {"title": "India's proptech intelligence layer: Aurum Analytica's AI-first bet starts paying off, reports strong growth in FY26", "para": "As the real estate sector embraces technology at an unprecedented pace, Aurum Analytica is leading the charge \u2014 turning artificial intelligence from a buzzwor